               <msContents>
                  <summary change="#add-summary"> An undated <title>Qiṣṣah-ʼi Chahār Darvīsh</title>
                     (Tale of Four Dervishes) often erroneously attributed to medieval poet Amīr
                     Khusraw Dihlavī (ca. 1253–1325); however, the text likely dates much
                     later.</summary>

                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_515-item1">
                     <author role="dub" key="person_76503034" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/76503034/">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Amīr Khusraw Dihlavī, ca.
                           1253-1325</persName>; <lb/><persName xml:lang="fa">امير خسرو <addName
